<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Michigan Web Design for Small Businesses | Olivia Arkema</title>
<meta name="description" content="Simple, fast websites for Michigan small businesses. Designed to generate leads, build trust, and be easy to maintain.">

<link rel="icon" href="green_bow.png">

<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="font-[Inter] bg-[#f4efe9] text-[#2f2f2f]">

<!-- NAV -->
<header id="navbar" class="fixed w-full z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur border-b border-[#e6dfd7]">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">

    <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold">OA</a>

    <nav class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 text-sm">
      <a href="/#home">Home</a>
      <a href="/#services">Work</a>
      <a href="/#clients">Projects</a>
      <a href="/#featuredwork">Writing</a>
      <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <button id="menuBtn" class="md:hidden text-2xl">☰</button>
  </div>

  <div id="mobileMenu" class="hidden px-6 pb-4 bg-white border-t border-[#e6dfd7]">
    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4 text-sm pt-4">
      <a href="/#home">Home</a>
      <a href="/#services">Work</a>
      <a href="/#clients">Projects</a>
      <a href="/#featuredwork">Writing</a>
      <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<script>
menuBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
  mobileMenu.classList.toggle("hidden");
});
</script>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="min-h-[80vh] flex items-center text-center bg-[#1f3a4a] text-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">

    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-6 font-[Prata]">
      Web Design for Michigan Small Businesses
    </h1>

    <p class="mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto text-white/80">
      Simple, fast websites that help you get more calls, customers, and repeat business.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/#clients" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-lg border border-white">
        View Work
      </a>

      <a href="/contact" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[#c6d86d] text-[#0d3921] font-medium">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT YOU NEED -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">

    <h2 class="text-3xl mb-6 font-[Prata]">What You Actually Need</h2>

    <p class="text-[#6f6a5f] mb-6">
      Most agencies overcomplicate things. You don’t need a massive custom build or dozens of pages.
    </p>

    <p class="text-[#6f6a5f]">
      You need a fast, clear website that builds trust and makes it easy for customers to contact you.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section class="py-24 bg-[#f4efe9]">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">

    <h2 class="text-4xl mb-12 font-[Prata]">What I Do</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <div class="card p-8 text-left rounded-xl">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Web Design & Development</h3>
        <p class="text-[#6f6a5f]">
          Clean, modern websites built to convert—not just look good.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8 text-left rounded-xl">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Local SEO Foundations</h3>
        <p class="text-[#6f6a5f]">
          Structured so customers in your area can actually find you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8 text-left rounded-xl">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Messaging & Structure</h3>
        <p class="text-[#6f6a5f]">
          Clear layout and copy so visitors understand what you do instantly.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- BEFORE / AFTER -->
<section class="py-24 bg-[#f4efe9]">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">

    <h2 class="text-4xl mb-6 font-[Prata]">Real Results</h2>

    <p class="mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto text-[#6f6a5f]">
      A recent redesign for a Michigan-based business.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

      <!-- BEFORE -->
      <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20201101143613/https://www.sdgprecisionag.com/" target="_blank"
         class="group border border-[#e6dfd7] p-6 rounded-xl text-left transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md">

        <p class="text-xs mb-2 text-[#6f6a5f]">BEFORE</p>

        <h3 class="mb-3">Outdated, hard to navigate</h3>

        <div class="aspect-video bg-[#e6dfd7] rounded mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-[#6f6a5f]">
          View old site
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <span class="text-sm text-[#6f6a5f]">Open archive</span>
          <span class="text-xl group-hover:translate-x-1 transition">→</span>
        </div>

      </a>

      <!-- AFTER -->
      <a href="https://www.sdgprecisionag.com" target="_blank"
         class="group border border-[#e6dfd7] p-6 rounded-xl text-left transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md">

        <p class="text-xs mb-2 text-[#6f6a5f]">AFTER</p>

        <h3 class="mb-3">Clean, clear, and built to convert</h3>

        <div class="aspect-video bg-[#e6dfd7] rounded mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-[#6f6a5f]">
          View new site
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <span class="text-sm text-[#6f6a5f]">Visit site</span>
          <span class="text-xl group-hover:translate-x-1 transition">→</span>
        </div>

      </a>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">

    <h2 class="text-3xl mb-6 font-[Prata]">Who This Is For</h2>

    <p class="text-[#6f6a5f]">
      Small businesses across Michigan—especially service businesses, contractors, local shops, and independent professionals—who want a professional online presence without the complexity.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- APPROACH -->
<section class="py-24 bg-[#f4efe9]">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">

    <h2 class="text-3xl mb-10 text-center font-[Prata]">Simple Process</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

      <div class="card p-6 rounded-xl">
        <h3 class="mb-2">1. Understand</h3>
        <p class="text-[#6f6a5f]">Your business, customers, and goals.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6 rounded-xl">
        <h3 class="mb-2">2. Structure</h3>
        <p class="text-[#6f6a5f]">Clear layout that guides action.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6 rounded-xl">
        <h3 class="mb-2">3. Build</h3>
        <p class="text-[#6f6a5f]">Fast, responsive, and easy to maintain.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6 rounded-xl">
        <h3 class="mb-2">4. Launch</h3>
        <p class="text-[#6f6a5f]">Set up for long-term growth.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- MICHIGAN -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">

    <h2 class="text-3xl mb-6 font-[Prata]">Built for Michigan Businesses</h2>

    <p class="text-[#6f6a5f]">
      I work with businesses across Michigan, especially in West Michigan communities like Manistee, Ludington, Traverse City, and Grand Rapids.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="py-20 bg-[#1f3a4a] text-white text-center">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">

    <h2 class="text-3xl mb-6 font-[Prata]">Let’s build something that works.</h2>

    <p class="mb-8 text-white/80">
      If your website isn’t doing much—or you don’t have one yet—I can help.
    </p>

    <a href="/contact" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[#c6d86d] text-[#0d3921] font-medium">
      Get in Touch
    </a>

  </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
